Just today it seems, the format of issues in the Backlog has changed, moving the ticket number over far to the right.

This change is terrible. Ticket numbers are one of the most important parts of the way the we work. Our sprints are generally comprised of MANY different projects, and seeing the ticket number clearly, well-separated from a lot of other visual information is just critical.

Is this configurable in some way of which I am not aware? If not, please make it configurable or give me the option to switch back. The way it is today is a real impediment.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-63537].
