Hi guys. 

 

When scrumming, meeting, or even thinking - users read left to right. Even with concise ticket names, it's SO much easier to talk about a ticket by referring to it's identifier first. These have now been moved to the right of the backlog, and this makes it very unintuitive when your brain is trying to match IDs and names. 

 

Please can you revert this change, or at least make it configurable?

